pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: content-left-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 6, 720]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: content-top-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 1280, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: content-section-name
    elementType: text
    bounds: [900, 16, 340, 22]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: 05 结论与研究展望

  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 24, 840, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 26
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>核心研究贡献与未来展望</strong></p>

  - elementId: title-separator
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 68, 1200, 1]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$borderGray"

  # 三个核心贡献
  - elementId: contrib-1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 86, 366, 260]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: contrib-1-icon-area
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 86, 366, 64]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#123960"

  - elementId: contrib-1-icon-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 86, 366, 64]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF88"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: CONTRIBUTION 01

  - elementId: contrib-1-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 162, 334, 170]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p><strong>轻量化模型架构</strong></p>
        <p>提出了首个适用于 XX 场景的轻量化模型，将参数量降低 40% 的同时保持 SOTA 级别精度，推理速度提升 3 倍</p>

  - elementId: contrib-2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [457, 86, 366, 260]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$secondary"

  - elementId: contrib-2-icon-area
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [457, 86, 366, 64]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#3A6A9A"

  - elementId: contrib-2-icon-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [457, 86, 366, 64]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF88"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: CONTRIBUTION 02

  - elementId: contrib-2-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [473, 162, 334, 170]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p><strong>高质量标注数据集</strong></p>
        <p>构建了包含 10K+ 样本的高质量标注数据集，已开源并被多个后续工作引用，填补了该领域的数据空白</p>

  - elementId: contrib-3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [874, 86, 366, 260]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: contrib-3-icon-area
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [874, 86, 366, 64]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#1E6A7E"

  - elementId: contrib-3-icon-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [874, 86, 366, 64]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF88"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: CONTRIBUTION 03

  - elementId: contrib-3-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [890, 162, 334, 170]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p><strong>工业级部署验证</strong></p>
        <p>在 AA 企业完成工业级部署验证，系统稳定运行超过 6 个月，日均处理请求 100 万+，效果达到预期</p>

  # 未来展望区域
  - elementId: future-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 376, 400, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>未来研究方向</strong></p>

  - elementId: future-sep
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 410, 1200, 1]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$borderGray"

  - elementId: future-1
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 428, 370, 100]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightGray"

  - elementId: future-1-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 438, 338, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p><strong>少样本学习</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#888888">探索少样本/零样本场景下的适应性方法，降低标注成本依赖</p>

  - elementId: future-2
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [455, 428, 370, 100]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightGray"

  - elementId: future-2-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [471, 438, 338, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p><strong>多模态融合</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#888888">引入多模态信息进一步提升模型表征能力，实现跨模态知识迁移</p>

  - elementId: future-3
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [870, 428, 370, 100]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightGray"

  - elementId: future-3-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [886, 438, 338, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 15
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p><strong>行业迁移</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size:14px; color:#888888">研究模型在医疗、金融、教育等垂直行业场景中的迁移与适配能力</p>

  # 底部学术引用提示
  - elementId: ref-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 556, 1200, 80]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#E3F0FA"

  - elementId: ref-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 562, 1160, 68]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p><strong>已发表成果：</strong>本研究相关论文已被 [会议/期刊名] 录用（CCF-A 类），代码与数据集已在 GitHub 开源，获得 500+ Star。</p>
        <p><strong>引用格式：</strong>Author et al., "Title of the Paper," in Proc. of [Conference], 2024, pp. xxx-xxx.</p>

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1200, 680, 50, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "9"
